text: Schöndorf is the name of two municipalities in Germany: * Schöndorf, Rhineland-Palatinate, in the Trier-Saarburg district, Rhineland-Palatinate * Schöndorf, Thuringia, in the Saale-Orla-Kreis, Thuringia and to: * Schöndorf, the German name for Frumușeni Commune, Arad County, Romania == Other == * Schondorf am Ammersee, a municipality in the district of Landsberg am Lech, Bavaria
title: Schöndorf
